Important guidelines:
1. Return ONLY a JSON object mapping each slot type to a list of exact text spans from the query
2. Use exact substrings - copy the text precisely as it appears in the query (preserve the original capitalization)
3. Omit slot types that do not occur in the query
4. Do NOT include articles (a, an, the) unless they are part of a proper restaurant name
5. Restaurant_Name should include the word "restaurant" if it appears immediately adjacent to the name in the query
