7. Restaurant names (e.g., "McDonald's", "Olive Garden") should be tagged as Restaurant_Name
8. Dishes are specific food items (e.g., "pizza", "sauce", "burger")
9. Rating includes quality descriptors like "highly rated", "5 star", "best"
